data.text: The exit poll released back in 2016 between Pedro Pablo Kuczynski and Keiko Fujimori was 50.4% to 49.6% in Kuczynski's favor. The final result was 50.1% to 49.9%. Based on those results, Fujimori might be the winner of this election.... not a sweeping endorsement #Elecciones2021
